WEBVTT

00:00.324 --> 00:02.840
Lorenzo's lost blood, I'm
gonna give him some of mine.

00:02.841 --> 00:04.842
I feared I'd lost you.
Where am I?

00:04.910 --> 00:06.844
You're where you belong.

00:06.912 --> 00:09.780
There is goodness in you,
there is grace.

00:09.848 --> 00:12.616
No one looks on me
and sees grace.

00:12.684 --> 00:14.218
I do.

00:14.286 --> 00:16.554
Storm on the way, could push us
into the rocks.

00:16.621 --> 00:18.622
This is not how I saw us finding
your new world.

00:20.225 --> 00:23.461
Nico!
Not everyone abandoned him.

00:23.528 --> 00:28.132
You dare enter Naples unannounced
and meet with my wife in secret?

00:28.200 --> 00:31.969
All must earn a seat
at my table.

00:32.037 --> 00:33.204
Call it a game.

00:33.271 --> 00:35.172
Make me a full partner
in your plan.

00:35.240 --> 00:38.442
The Sword of Osman Gazi.
I'm taking it with me.

00:38.510 --> 00:41.078
They came here when
I was just a little girl.

00:41.146 --> 00:43.013
We called them the Sun
and the Moon.

00:43.081 --> 00:45.216
It is her face
I see in yours.

00:45.283 --> 00:48.385
She came for the Book of Leaves.
My mother.

